This field contains the raw HTML of angular advertisement. You may use any HTML you like - BB code is not accepted here.<br /><br />If you want to refer by name to a user who viewing this angular advertisement, include {username} in the text of angular advertisement and it will be replaced with the user's username when angular advertisement is displayed to them.<br /><br />You may inculude {pmunead} and {vmunread} to your HTML contents which <em>{pmunread}</em> refer to count of unread private messages and <em>{vmunread}</em> refer to count of unread visitor messages of the logged in user.<br /><br />You may also use {userid} and {sessionurl} to assist in creating hyperlinks.